---
import DocsLayout from '../layouts/DocsLayout.astro';
---

<DocsLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="EGCSite privacy policy. No personal data collected. No cookies. GoatCounter analytics only."
  current="privacy"
>

  <div class="pb-2 mb-8 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800">
    <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-egc-600 dark:text-egc-400 mb-2">Legal</p>
    <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
      Effective date: June 16, 2026. Last updated: June 16, 2026.
    </p>
  </div>

  <section class="mb-10 prose prose-sm dark:prose-invert max-w-none">

    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-6">
      This site (<strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white">fmarzochi.github.io/EGCSite</strong>) is the official documentation and marketing website for
      <a href="https://github.com/Fmarzochi/EGC" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-egc-600 dark:text-egc-400 hover:underline">EGC - Extended Global Context</a>,
      an open-source project. This policy explains what data is collected when you visit this site.
    </p>

    <!-- TL;DR card -->
    <div class="rounded-xl border border-egc-500/20 bg-egc-500/5 dark:bg-egc-500/10 p-5 mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-base font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">TL;DR</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-egc-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0">✓</span> No personal data collected</li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-egc-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0">✓</span> No cookies, no tracking pixels, no fingerprinting</li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-egc-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0">✓</span> No account or registration required</li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-egc-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0">✓</span> Analytics are aggregate-only and privacy-first</li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-egc-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0">✓</span> No data is sold or shared with third parties</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">What we collect</h2>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-6">
      We collect <strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white">no personal data</strong>. There are no forms, no login, no newsletter signup, and no user accounts on this site.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Analytics</h2>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">
      This site uses <a href="https://www.goatcounter.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-egc-600 dark:text-egc-400 hover:underline">GoatCounter</a>,
      an open-source, privacy-first analytics tool. GoatCounter:
    </p>
    <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-4 ml-4">
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="shrink-0">-</span> Does <strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white">not</strong> use cookies</li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="shrink-0">-</span> Does <strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white">not</strong> collect IP addresses or any personally identifiable information</li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="shrink-0">-</span> Does <strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white">not</strong> fingerprint devices or browsers</li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="shrink-0">-</span> Collects only aggregate page view counts and referrer domains</li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="shrink-0">-</span> Is GDPR and LGPD compliant by design, requiring no consent banner</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-6">
      The analytics dashboard is hosted at <a href="https://egc.goatcounter.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-egc-600 dark:text-egc-400 hover:underline">egc.goatcounter.com</a>.
      GoatCounter's own privacy policy applies to data processed by their service.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">RSS feed</h2>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-6">
      This site provides an <a href="/EGCSite/rss.xml" class="text-egc-600 dark:text-egc-400 hover:underline">RSS feed</a> for release announcements.
      Subscribing to the RSS feed does not send any data to us. Your RSS reader fetches the feed file directly from GitHub Pages.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Third-party services</h2>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">This site loads resources from:</p>
    <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6 ml-4">
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="shrink-0">-</span> <strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Google Fonts</strong> (Inter typeface) - font files served from fonts.gstatic.com. Google's privacy policy applies.</li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="shrink-0">-</span> <strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white">GitHub Pages</strong> - the hosting provider. GitHub's privacy policy applies to page delivery.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">EGC itself (the CLI tool)</h2>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-6">
      The EGC tool installed on your machine is local-first. All state is stored in <code class="text-xs bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded font-mono">~/.egc/</code> on your device.
      Nothing is transmitted to external servers. See the <a href="https://github.com/Fmarzochi/EGC/blob/main/SECURITY.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-egc-600 dark:text-egc-400 hover:underline">Security policy</a> for details.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Contact</h2>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
      Questions about this policy? Email <a href="mailto:fmarzochi@gmail.com" class="text-egc-600 dark:text-egc-400 hover:underline">fmarzochi@gmail.com</a>
      or open an issue at <a href="https://github.com/Fmarzochi/EGCSite/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-egc-600 dark:text-egc-400 hover:underline">github.com/Fmarzochi/EGCSite</a>.
    </p>

  </section>

</DocsLayout>
